      "content": "# style editors with tailwind classes or scoped style tags\n\nTwo styling approaches for editors:\n\n1. **Tailwind classes** — Preferred. Apply utility classes directly to elements.\n2. **Scoped style tags** — When Tailwind is insufficient. Make selectors specific to the editor component to prevent global CSS leakage.\n\n```tsx\n// ✅ Tailwind\n<div className=\"flex gap-4 p-6 rounded-lg border\">\n\n// ✅ Scoped style tag\n<style>{`\n  .my-editor-name .custom-table { border-collapse: collapse; }\n  .my-editor-name .custom-table td { padding: 8px; }\n`}</style>\n\n// ❌ Unscoped — will affect the entire app\n<style>{`\n  table { border-collapse: collapse; }\n  td { padding: 8px; }\n`}</style>\n```\n\n---\n\nTopics:\n- [[editor patterns]]",
